We're -- We just...

35:56.555 --> 35:58.324
He's our son.

35:58.357 --> 36:00.326
You shouldn't feel bad.

36:00.359 --> 36:02.794
You did what you thought
was best for Liam.

36:02.828 --> 36:05.297
You love Liam.

36:05.331 --> 36:09.535
